Classes/ObjectUserDefaults.html.name: ObjectUserDefaults
Classes/ObjectUserDefaults.html.abstract: An object oriented wrapper UserDefaults. Initialize it like an UserDefaults. See ObjectUserDefaults.item(forKey:) for getting and setting values.

Classes/ObjectUserDefaultsItem.html.name: ObjectUserDefaultsItem
Classes/ObjectUserDefaultsItem.html.abstract: A class representing a value stored in UserDefaults or ObjectUserDefaults. The item can exist or not.
